text = "Build: 
Press a settlement and choose a building to place
Mine:
Gain 20 gold, plus an additional 20 pr gold mine you control
Smith:
Gain 2 armor, plus an additional 2 pr armor smith you control
Train:
each of your settlements with a training ground get 4 extra soldiers,
unless the settlement has more than 12 soldier
March:
Get one movement, plus an additional pr goat stable"

