text = "Move/attack:
Move your soldiers from one settlement to another. 
You can choose to bring your dark lord with them.
raid:
choose a settlement, destroy a building in it to gain 8 soldiers and 8 gold
Brutalize:
Choose a settlement, turn a building within into an effigy which spawns 4 sodiers each turn.
8 soldiers if you have the sorcercer dard lord and 1 armor if you have the black smith dark lord"

